name: 501 Original Fit Jeans
description: Classic blue jeans with a straight leg cut and a relaxed fit. Made of durable denim, they feature a timeless five-pocket design and button fly, ideal for casual wear or rugged use.

name: Cowboy Cut Original Fit Jean
description: Indigo-colored jeans with a slim fit around the waist and a durable, heavyweight fabric. Designed for durability and functionality, perfect for outdoor or workwear settings.

name: Classic Fit Khaki Pants
description: Classic khaki pants with a relaxed fit and straight leg. Made from soft, breathable cotton, they are versatile for office or casual settings.

name: Slim Fit Chino Pants
description: Navy chinos with a slim, modern fit. Lightweight fabric makes them comfortable for everyday wear, suitable for casual and semi-formal occasions.

name: Midi Wrap Dress
description: A floral print wrap dress that falls to mid-calf length. Features a flattering waist tie, flowy silhouette, and lightweight fabric, ideal for spring or summer outings.

name: Satin Slip Dress
description: Emerald green satin slip dress with a minimalist design. Silky texture and slim spaghetti straps make it ideal for evening or formal wear.

name: Bohemian Maxi Dress
description: A rust-colored bohemian maxi dress featuring a flowy design, intricate embroidery, and long sleeves. Perfect for festival wear or laid-back summer days.

name: A-Line Denim Skirt
description: Light blue A-line denim skirt with a high waist and button-front design. Versatile and casual, suitable for everyday wear during warmer months.

name: Pleated Mini Skirt
description: A black pleated mini skirt with a high waist and a structured fit. Trendy and stylish, ideal for casual outings or pairing with oversized tops.
